      <section eId="sec_CCP-253-1">
        <num>CCP 253.1</num>
        <heading>253.1. Â Pleadings; random assignment of cases</heading>
        <subsection eId="CCP-253-1__subsec_1">
          <num>(1)</num>
          <content>
            <p>By drawing indiscriminately from a pool containing designations of all sections or divisions of court in the particular jurisdiction in which the case is filed.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CCP-253-1__subsec_2">
          <num>(2)</num>
          <content>
            <p>By use of a properly programmed electronic device or computer programmed to randomly assign cases to any one of the sections or divisions of court in the particular jurisdiction in which the case is filed.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=111474</p>
        </authorialNote>
      </section>
